sources.title: Behemoth | Full Horror Movie | Josh Eisenberg | Halloween 2022
sources.description:
Behemoth - Josh Riverton spent 10 years working for a global chemical behemoth, notorious for their environmental dumping. When his daughter becomes ill, Josh is convinced the company is to blame. A confrontation with his boss, Woeland, turns violent, forcing Josh to take him hostage. As Josh holds him captive, he begins losing grasp on reality. Is Woeland more than he seems, or is it all in Josh's head? 
2021.  Stars: Josh Eisenberg, Paul Statman, Jennifer Churchich
